    %section
        %h2.s4 How it all comes together
        %p Now, at the beginning of each new product launch, we have a multidiscipliary kickoff with product, design, copy, and marketing. Together we decide the high-level components of the sandwich based on the product’s features, importance and marketing strategy. Then the designer and copywriter pair to create the page.
