        %p.large The engineering team is finalizing the new product detail page template. Already, it allows us to launch product pages 40% faster. Once the PDP is fully integrated into our CMS, it will remove its reliance on engineering entirely. At this point, we should be able to launch product pages 80% faster than our original launch speed. This will allow design and engineering to spend more time on more complex problems.

